name: Project 202
description: The PROJECT202 infrastructure is a Proof-Of-Stake (PoS) algorithm-based blockchain 3.0 system, with its own decentralized data centers located on various countries. The Spare equipment capacity which is not being utilized for servicing the cryptocurrency infrastructure can be rented out for use on our P202 Servers platform with payments rendered via the P202 Token. Transaction processing and the work of the entire infrastructure will be held on server equipment, scaling the transaction speed ability to 100,000 transactions per second or more.
